The type of event that occurred: 
        - 'view' (user views a property)
        - 'click' (user clicks on property or related element)
        - 'search' (user conducts a search)
        - 'filter' (user applies a filter to refine search results)

A nested dictionary containing additional details about the event:
        - 'device': The type of device used, e.g. 'desktop', 'mobile', 'tablet'
        - 'referrer': The source of the traffic, e.g 'google', 'direct', 'email', 'ad'
